sourcesContent:
<template>
    <v-navigation-drawer v-model="drawer" absolute temporary="">
        <v-list>
            <v-list-tile to="/">
                <v-list-tile-action>
                    <v-icon>home</v-icon>
                </v-list-tile-action>
                <v-list-tile-title>Home</v-list-tile-title>
            </v-list-tile>

            <v-list-group prepend-icon="shopping_basket"
                          >
                <template v-slot:activator>
                    <v-list-tile>
                        <v-list-tile-title>Categories</v-list-tile-title>
                    </v-list-tile>
                </template>
                <v-list-group no-action
                              sub-group
                >
                    <template v-slot:activator>
                        <v-list-tile>
                            <v-list-tile-title>Women</v-list-tile-title>
                        </v-list-tile>
                    </template>

                    <v-list-tile v-for="(woman, i) in women"
                                 :key="i"
                                 :to="woman[1]"
                                 >
                        <v-list-tile-title v-text="woman[0]"></v-list-tile-title>
                        <v-list-tile-action>
<!--                            <v-icon v-text="woman[1]"></v-icon>-->
                        </v-list-tile-action>
                    </v-list-tile>
                </v-list-group>

                <v-list-group no-action
                              sub-group>
                    <template v-slot:activator>
                        <v-list-tile>
                            <v-list-tile-title>Men</v-list-tile-title>
                        </v-list-tile>
                    </template>

                    <v-list-tile v-for="(man, i) in men"
                                 :key="i"
                                 :to="man[1]"
                                 >
                        <v-list-tile-title v-text="man[0]"></v-list-tile-title>
                        <v-list-tile-action>
<!--                            <v-icon v-text="man[1]"></v-icon>-->
                        </v-list-tile-action>
                    </v-list-tile>
                </v-list-group>
            </v-list-group>

            <v-list-tile to="/">
                <v-list-tile-action>
                    <v-icon>account_circle</v-icon>
                </v-list-tile-action>
                <v-list-tile-title>Account</v-list-tile-title>
            </v-list-tile>

            <v-list-group prepend-icon="system_update">
                    <template v-slot:activator>
                        <v-list-tile>
                            <v-list-tile-title>Updates</v-list-tile-title>
                        </v-list-tile>
                    </template>

                    <v-list-tile v-for="(update, i) in updates"
                                 :key="i"
                                 :to="update.path"
                                 v-on:click="_navigateTo(update.path)">

                        <v-list-tile-action>
                           <!-- <v-icon>system_update</v-icon> -->
                        </v-list-tile-action>
                        <v-list-tile-title v-text="update.title"></v-list-tile-title>
                    </v-list-tile>
                </v-list-group>
        </v-list>
    </v-navigation-drawer>
</template>

<script>
	export default {
		name: "Navbar",
		data()
		{
			return {
                women: [
                    ['Tops', '/category/Women-Tops'],
	                ['Bottoms', '/category/Women-Bottoms'],
                ],
				men: [
					['Tops', '/category/Men-Tops'],
					['Bottoms', '/category/Men-Bottoms'],
					['Accessories', '/category/Men-Accessories'],
                ],
                updates: [
                    {
                        path: '/update-without-skip-and-claim',
                        title: 'Default'
                    },
                    {
                        path: '/update-with-skip-no-claim',
                        title: 'Forced'
                    },
                    {
                        path: '/update-with-skip-and-claim',
                        title: 'Forced & immediate control'
                    },
                    {
                        path: '/single-client-update',
                        title: 'Single Client'
                    },
                    {
                        path: '/multi-client-update',
                        title: 'Multi Client'
                    }
				],
                drawer: false
			}
		},
        mounted()
        {
        	// this.bus.$on('toggleNavbar', this._toggleNavbar());
        },
        methods:
        {
        	_toggleNavbar()
            {
            	this.drawer = !this.drawer;
            },_navigateTo(url)
	        {
		        window.location = url;
	        },
        }
	}
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
